{"tid":1586860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田要抵制美心，唔係係門口鳩叫下，貼下文宣就得","createTime":"2019-09-22T07:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T09:03:41.000Z","uid":240935,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42265175562f370b3722957a8bc45c209a5c25ef","tid":1586860,"uid":240935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVHpSdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVHpSdd.png&h=23bfcfb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下simple life仲full緊場，証明無料到啦<br />\n<br />\nSimple life員工教路，間野唔限時，無最低消費，早d去排隊，一人一張枱，求其叫最平既野，坐佢成晚<br />\n佢地無得搭枱，唔會跟人數安排枱，係先到先得果隻<br />\n即係佢無哂細枱既話。你去到就算一位，都要比張大枱你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n門口叫抵制無用，就要用最低成本去影響佢地個生意額"},{"pid":"98a6521f3a0c5402908591f52dc8330a3871947a","tid":1586860,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"淨叫杯水得唔得"},{"pid":"ab7b960fb09fb7ed12ceb930bbcc711153bcbe08","tid":1586860,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"入去坐晒啲位<br />\n<br />\n但轉頭又會有失敗撚開 post 話美心好好生意"},{"pid":"66afab243caad537eb015852883cb6e09c130cf6","tid":1586860,"uid":240935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7b960fb09fb7ed12ceb930bbcc711153bcbe08","tid":1586860,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"入去坐晒啲位<br />\n<br />\n但轉頭又會有失敗撚開 post 話美心好好生意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:15:53.000Z","msg":"一人一張枱會有幾好生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要全部黑衫"},{"pid":"a5eeaed64d9c1fc64d5e57ae1c39879a320b4fcd","tid":1586860,"uid":240935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a6521f3a0c5402908591f52dc8330a3871947a","tid":1586860,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"淨叫杯水得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-